OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FMost areas
OL,6,Fwill have a dry, warm and largely
OL,7,Fclear night with light winds. However,
OL,8,Fthe north and west of Scotland will
OL,9,Fsee cloudier skies with some patchy
OL,10,Frain. A few fog patches affecting
OL,11,FNorthern Ireland and southwest
OL,12,FScotland.
OL,13,
OL,14,CMonday:FHigh pressure dominates the
OL,15,Fweather on Bank Holiday Monday,
OL,16,Fbringing mostly dry and sunny
OL,17,Fconditions . The potential for record
OL,18,Fbreaking May temperatures. Northwest
OL,19,FScotland remains cooler with patchy
OL,20,Frain.
